data.description: PROPERTY SHOWINGS ARE BY APPOINTMENT ONLY.  SHOW TO PRE-QUALIFIED BUYERS ONLY.  PRE-QUAL LETTER SHOULD BE PRESENTED TO LISTING AGENT PRIOR TO SHOWING.    Welcome to this magnificent home nestled within the confines of a prestigious Friendship Estates neighborhood, this 9,470-square-foot; five level colonial home stands as a timeless testament to architectural grandeur and luxurious living. Majestic columns frame the entrance, leading into a grand foyer setting the tone for opulence.  The kitchen is equipped with state-of-the-art appliances and granite countertops, marble flooring serves as the heart of the home, inviting culinary indulgence, a masterpiece of architectural custom design, brilliance and opulent living; elegant hardwood floors guide you through the meticulously designed living spaces, where expansive windows bathe each room in natural light, accentuating the meticulous craftsmanship that defines every corner.  Situated in a sought-after prestigious neighborhood, this residence combines classic sophistication with modern amenities for the ultimate in luxury living. Key Features: Grand Entryway: A sweeping staircase leads to the impressive main entrance adorned with  custom iron double doors, setting the tone for the grandeur within. Spacious Living Areas: Expansive living and entertainment spaces on each level, featuring high ceilings, exquisite detailing, and large windows bathing the interiors in natural light. Gourmet Kitchen: State-of-the-art chef's kitchen equipped with top-tier appliances, granite countertops, Master Suite: A lavish master suite occupying an entire level, complete with a private balcony, walk-in closets, and a spa-like en-suite bathroom.  The master suite is a sanctuary of tranquility, featuring a private balcony; a spa-like ensuite bathroom, and two sprawling walk-in closets. Theater Room: A dedicated  theater/entertainment room with audio-visual technology for an immersive cinematic speakers experience. Additional Kitchenette in Basement - Additional rooms can flex to den/bedroom with basement entrance. Outdoor Gazebo with HotTub: Enjoy year-round relaxation with an covered HotTub featuring direct access to a private outdoor patio. Fitness Center: Stay fit in style with a fully equipped gym, offering mirrored views and inspiring spaces for workouts. Smart Home Technology: Integrated smart home thermostat systems for effortless control of heating and air-conditioning. Outdoor Oasis: Patio with outdoor kitchen overlooking manicured  yard, providing outdoor spaces for relaxation and entertaining. Security and Privacy: State-of-the-art security system, with cameras ensuring peace of mind for maximum privacy. Garage Space: Ample 3-car garage space for multiple vehicles (oversized spacing), with additional parking options available.  This exceptional custom colonial offers an unparalleled combination of luxury, comfort, and style. Whether you seek refined entertaining spaces, relaxation in the hot tub, or the convenience of comfortable home living, this residence fulfills the highest expectations of modern living. Experience the epitome of elegance in every corner of this 5-level masterpiece.   Additional bedrooms boast their own en-suite bathrooms; and a Jack and Jill Bathroom ensuring comfort and privacy for all.  Entertainment finds its zenith in the home's lower level, where a fully equipped theater/entertainment room and stylish bar await another totally separate entertainment room. The outdoor oasis beckons with a sprawling patio, and lush landscaping, creating an ideal backdrop for soirées and gatherings.  With its classical exterior and modern interiors, this colonial masterpiece seamlessly blends timeless elegance with contemporary comfort, providing a haven of sophistication in the heart of a coveted neighborhood.
